IT security issues: the need for end user oriented research
Considerable attention has been given to the technical and policy issues
	involved with IT security issues in recent years. The growth of
	e-commerce and the Internet, as well as widely publicized hacker
	attacks, have brought IT security into prominent focus and routine
	corporate attention. Yet, much more research is needed from the end
	user (EU) perspective. This position paper is a call for such research
	and outlines some possible directions of interest
